                    <ul class="support">
                        <li><p>FAQ</p></li>
                        <li><p>Payment Option</p></li>
                        <li><p>Booking Tips</p></li>
                        <li><p>Information</p></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3">
                    <h4 class="title" style="color: #B0413E">Get Our <strong>Newsletter </strong></h4>
                    <p>I love you go to the moon and back</p>

                    <div class="fb-page col-md-4"
